{"tid":1398724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全世界入黎]罷工、罷買、罷市。上中下路缺一不可","createTime":"2019-08-03T02:22:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:14:14.000Z","uid":288182,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc9fccfde1d34a6cd22b6ac2bfb9c288175089e","tid":1398724,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"首先，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係叫大家唔好罷工</strong></span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>但係要精準地罷工</strong></span></span>。<br />\n大家自己問下自己，你份工唔返一日，隔離位會唔會做埋你個份？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定係第二日你自己返去做返自己D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果係後者，你罷乜工，你叫暫緩工作</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">罷工要有成效，一定要係前線市民，例如巴士、地鐵車長，甚至清潔工、垃圾車車長、速遞員。<br />\n大家返BACK OFFICE文職人員，罷一日、你罷黎做乜。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係叫你文職食花生，唔罷工、你可以捐人工，支援前線日薪、手停口停的罷工前線提供生活資助</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工唔係一日半日，最後一定到你文職參與，但唔係第一個出黎罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>全城罷買！！</strong></span></span>，所有和理非唔好同我講你做唔到，每個人都可以參與。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係叫你絕食，係罷娛樂消費，飲食限消費(每人每餐$50以下)</span></strong></span>，你阻兩班地鐵重創唔到經濟。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">作為消費者，你有權選擇如何消費！冇人可以質疑你</span></strong></span><br />\n都係個句廢話，爭取商界發聲，你食100個催淚彈都見唔到林鄭，人地溝通渠道多你好多。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你食完催淚彈後走去打個紅底邊爐，紅底老闆再捐返100萬比警隊招呼你</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你衝乜？<br />\n<br />\n當民氣足，先最後有機會全民罷市，罷市一定要無限期，作為終極手段。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非各光譜，罷工、罷買、罷市。兄弟爬山，風雨同路。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8d7f13af255d7eb755c6c04c7da9316c19cdcd","tid":1398724,"uid":52566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQHBGKp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQHBGKp.png&h=7281096a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28K08pq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28K08pq.png&h=bd07ca68&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAx2ChM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAx2ChM.png&h=2dfbfa1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08034b280ab707e927280be82636e0617db4f69d","tid":1398724,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"我知道香港好多人都係和理非，既然硬碰硬比較難做到，咁破壞香港經濟亦未嘗唔係一個好方法，破壞經濟對一個政權嚟講亦係一個毀滅性打擊，中共作為一個極權，好多錢都會放咗喺維穏費度，既然佢都係用啲錢去對付返人民，我地亦冇必要幫佢維持經濟發展<br />\n<br />\n#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"c773e00ab1f514e9cc55d84f0fa3f97e981daccf","tid":1398724,"uid":103553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"借位一推<br />\n<br />\n真。罷工X港鐵不合作運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1394878/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1394878/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3877c5b95e4a5a47b34fc2949262dd57b114517e","tid":1398724,"uid":250321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:27:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b99d6a537749babc4592b031f01c62e9a9733c2","tid":1398724,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"繼續推到上太空"},{"pid":"5cfff95548a16d8f24beac32ea3960756ca90d9b","tid":1398724,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:35:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"91db838fedbc40edfb1dd01214979e439e0c9eef","tid":1398724,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:47:32.000Z","msg":"繼續推到上太空"},{"pid":"5e5c0fb1d8092833d75bcb58abd6be4ef7bc6385","tid":1398724,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T02:57:06.000Z","msg":"繼續推到上太空"},{"pid":"9b3513f29443fd31aa3c3eb29ecfeeebec8c6982","tid":1398724,"uid":288182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:14:14.000Z","msg":"推多次"}]}